Package: robvis
Title: Quickly Visualise The Results Of Risk-Of-Bias (ROB) Assessments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Luke", "McGuinness",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "luke.mcguinness@bristol.ac.uk"),
    person("Emily", "Kothe", role = "ctb")          )
Description: This package allows for the visualisation of risk-of-bias assessments performed using three major tools: ROB2.0 (for randomised controlled trials), ROBINS-I (for non-randomised studies of interventions), and QUADAS-2 (for diagnostic accuracy studies).
